      <title>摩根大通关注液化天然气实物交易，因戴蒙称赞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/jpmorgan-eyes-physical-lng-trading-again-after-dimon-hails-boon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司 (JPMorgan Chase &amp; Co.) 正在就重启液化天然气实物交易进行谈判，此前该公司已暂停了该交易十多年，此举符合其首席执行官杰米·戴蒙 (Jamie Dimon) 增加国内产量和能源出口的呼吁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/jpmorgan-eyes-physical-lng-trading-again-after-dimon-hails-boon</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
